Package nl.codevs.strinput.examples.spigotmc

package nl.codevs.strinput.examples.spigotmc
Spigot plugin implementation using this commands system.
Main classes to pay attention to:
  • SpigotPlugin An example of an implemented plugin class with the command system.
  • SpigotCenter The command center which is attached to the main class of a plugin.
  • SpigotUser A user implementation with functions to send messages and derivatives to a player.
  • nl.codevs.strinput.examples.spigotmc.extensions Extensions to the parameter parsing and context handling
Since:
v0.1
